      "comment": "KNEEL DOWN (1) turns up back sharply in trip having failed to keep up with a plugging seventh over 900m at Wellington. Extra trip in his favour from the good draw. Improver. INDI SPRINGS (6) returns from a four-month break after showing ability in her first prep. Ran second on debut, then struggled to close off with a poor fifth over 1100m at this track. Looks ready to go following a trial win at Wellington. Capable of getting off the mark. MITAKA (7) returns from a lengthy break. Plagued by wide barriers when last in work and primed for this with the two trials. Nicely placed and can figure in the finish. INFINITE VIXON (5) Denman mare on debut for the Mulholland stable. Finished second in her latest trial over 1000m at Mudgee. Keep safe with the claim.",
